original: This is a description of testing armband.
english: This is a description of testing armband.

original: Light blue shoulder tape with a patch of United Nations troops in Chernarus.
english: Light blue shoulder tape with a patch of United Nations troops in Chernarus.
czech: Světle modrá páska přes rameno s nášivkou jednotek Organizace Spojených Národů v Černarusi.

original: Blue shoulder tape with Trade Union print. It does not guarantee the credibility of the wearer.
english: Blue shoulder tape with Trade Union print. It does not guarantee the credibility of the wearer.
czech: Modrá páska přes rameno s potiskem Obchodní unie. Nezaručuje důvěryhodnost nositele.

original: Green shoulder tape with National Party applique. Long live Chernarus!
english: Green shoulder tape with National Party applique. Sláva Černarusi!
czech: Zelená páska přes rameno s nášivkou Národní Strany. Ať žije Černarus!

original: Red shoulder tape with a patch of the Chernarussian Movement of Red Star.
english: Red armband with a patch of the Chernarussian Movement of Red Star.
czech: Rudá páska přes rameno s nášivkou Černaruského hnutí Rudé hvězdy.

original: Shoulder tape in the colors of the Republic of Poland's flag.
english: Shoulder tape in the colors of the Republic of Poland's flag
czech: Páska přes rameno v barvách Polské republiky.

original: Green shoulder tape with a patch of the Chernarussian Defense Forces.
english: Green shoulder tape with a patch of the Chernarussian Defense Forces.
czech: Zelená páska přes rameno s nášivkou Černaruských ozbrojených sil.

original: This shoulder tape holds a memory of a beloved comrade survivor from Czechia. A pioneer of altruistic RP, not a selfish man, we've lost on our way. Long live Jack Forest! Shall his name be remembered by the new blood!
english: This shoulder tape holds a memory of a beloved comrade survivor from Czechia. A pioneer of altruistic RP, not a selfish man, we've lost on our way. Long live Jack Forest! Shall his name be remembered by the new blood!
czech: Ztracená páska přes rameno s mužským jménem. Kde je Jack?

original: Black shoulder tape. Who are Bren's Ravens? I'm in fear!
english: Black shoulder tape. Who are Bren's Ravens? I'm in fear!
czech: Páska přes rameno. Kdo jsou Brenovy Havrani? Mám strach!

original: Tape over the shoulder of the Chernarussian Patriotic Union. Glory to the New Republic!
english: Tape over the shoulder of the Chernarussian Patriotic Union. Glory to the New Republic!
czech: Páska přes rameno Vlastenecké Unie. Sláva Nové Republice!

original: Tape over the shoulder of the Novy Sobor Militia. Bow to your knees!
english: Tape over the shoulder of the Novy Sobor Militia. Bow to your knees!
czech: Páska přes rameno Novosoborské Milice. Klaňte se ke kolenou!

original: You know, I am kind of a priest myself ...
english: You know, I am kind of a priest myself ...
czech: Víte, taky jsem tak trochu kněz ...
Páska přes rameno koaličního spolku na území Kamenky a okolí.

original: This shoulder tape speaks for itself.
english: This shoulder tape speaks for itself.
czech: Jde z té pásky strach, co víc k tomu dodat ...
